	<main class="container-fluid">
        <div class="text-light">
            <h5>How to use</h5>
            Send message named <code>detect_faces</code> via WebSocket (this_url/socket.io) containing base64 image captured from the camera.<br>
            Request body structure:
            <code>{frame: &lt;your image as base64&gt;, width: &lt;W&gt;, height: &lt;H&gt;}</code><br>
            Response body structure:
            <code>[boxes array] or None</code><br>
        </div>
	</main>
